cs.SP, cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NA 

The paper deals with signal processing and optimization problems, which are common topics in the sub-categories of cs.SP (Signal Processing), cs.IT (Information Theory), and cs.NA (Numerical Analysis). The use of sparse models and convex optimization methods also suggests the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
